docs.title: Character Typing Game using TypeScript
docs.text: This app is a typing game that asks users to type the character on the screen. It uses TypeScript for type-checking and type annotations.

docs.title: Getting Started
docs.text:
git clone https://github.com/lulunac27a/typescript-character-typing-game.git
cd typescript-character-typing-game
npm install
npm run compile
npm run start
